{"image_id": "VRSN_2011_page_103", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "VERISIGN, INC.", "bbox": [540.6, 140.2, 697.4, 161.0]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS—(Continued)", "bbox": [279.5, 177.7, 958.7, 198.5]}, {"text": "DECEMBER 31, 2011, 2010 AND 2009", "bbox": [445.2, 215.2, 792.7, 236.0]}, {"text": "During 2010, the Company recorded a $7.8 million tax expense, reflecting a remeasurement of state", "bbox": [185.5, 265.4, 1020.9, 286.3]}, {"text": "deferred tax assets and liabilities using future tax rates which will be in effect when the underlying assets and", "bbox": [143.8, 290.4, 1056.8, 311.3]}, {"text": "liabilities will reverse. The change in state tax rate is primarily attributable to the change in the Company’s", "bbox": [143.8, 315.4, 1037.2, 336.3]}, {"text": "business operations after the sale of the Authentication Services business.", "bbox": [143.8, 340.5, 758.5, 361.3]}, {"text": "During 2009, the State of California enacted changes in tax laws that were expected to have a beneficial", "bbox": [185.5, 386.2, 1053.7, 407.0]}, {"text": "impact on the Company’s effective tax rate beginning in 2011. As a result, the Company revalued its state", "bbox": [143.8, 411.2, 1029.1, 432.0]}, {"text": "deferred tax assets that are expected to reverse after the effective date of the change, and recognized an income", "bbox": [143.8, 436.2, 1071.0, 457.1]}, {"text": "tax benefit of $4.9 million in state taxes for 2009.", "bbox": [143.8, 461.2, 557.4, 482.1]}, {"text": "During 2009, the California Franchise Tax Board agreed with certain Company positions during the", "bbox": [185.5, 507.0, 1020.1, 527.8]}, {"text": "Franchise Tax Board’s audit of the years ended December 31, 2003 to December 31, 2005. The Company", "bbox": [143.8, 532.0, 1027.4, 552.8]}, {"text": "recorded an income tax benefit of $3.4 million in state taxes in 2009.", "bbox": [143.8, 557.0, 719.1, 577.8]}, {"text": "The tax effects of temporary differences that give rise to significant portions of the Company’s deferred tax", "bbox": [185.5, 602.7, 1083.4, 623.6]}, {"text": "assets and liabilities are as follows:", "bbox": [143.8, 627.7, 437.9, 648.6]}, {"text": "As of December 31,", "bbox": [929.6, 668.2, 1067.6, 684.8]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [928.9, 693.2, 962.3, 709.8]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [1034.9, 693.2, 1068.2, 709.8]}, {"text": "(In thousands)", "bbox": [947.0, 718.2, 1050.3, 734.8]}, {"text": "Deferred tax assets:", "bbox": [143.8, 740.2, 308.4, 761.0]}, {"text": "Net operating loss carryforwards . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 765.2, 882.2, 786.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [903.1, 765.2, 913.5, 786.0]}, {"text": "20,157", "bbox": [930.9, 765.2, 988.2, 786.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1009.1, 765.2, 1019.5, 786.0]}, {"text": "20,376", "bbox": [1036.9, 765.2, 1094.2, 786.0]}, {"text": "Deductible goodwill and intangible assets . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 790.2, 882.2, 811.0]}, {"text": "8,909", "bbox": [941.3, 790.2, 988.2, 811.0]}, {"text": "10,354", "bbox": [1036.9, 790.2, 1094.2, 811.0]}, {"text": "Tax credit carryforwards . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 815.2, 882.2, 836.0]}, {"text": "6,213", "bbox": [941.3, 815.2, 988.2, 836.0]}, {"text": "7,866", "bbox": [1047.3, 815.2, 1094.2, 836.0]}, {"text": "Deferred revenue, accruals and reserves . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 840.2, 882.2, 861.0]}, {"text": "106,234", "bbox": [920.5, 840.2, 988.2, 861.0]}, {"text": "96,433", "bbox": [1036.9, 840.2, 1094.2, 861.0]}, {"text": "Capital loss carryforwards and book impairment of investments . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 865.2, 882.2, 886.0]}, {"text": "5,749", "bbox": [941.3, 865.2, 988.2, 886.0]}, {"text": "5,759", "bbox": [1047.3, 865.2, 1094.2, 886.0