90,125)", "bbox": [913.5, 1090.3, 995.1, 1111.1]}, {"text": "(359,123)", "bbox": [1019.5, 1090.3, 1101.1, 1111.1]}, {"text": "Other . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 1115.3, 882.2, 1136.1]}, {"text": "(3,417)", "bbox": [934.3, 1115.3, 995.1, 1136.1]}, {"text": "(4,210)", "bbox": [1040.3, 1115.3, 1101.1, 1136.1]}, {"text": "Total deferred tax liabilities . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [227.2, 1148.6, 882.2, 1169.5]}, {"text": "(393,732)", "bbox": [913.5, 1148.6, 995.1, 1169.5]}, {"text": "(366,248)", "bbox": [1019.5, 1148.6, 1101.1, 1169.5]}, {"text": "Total net deferred tax liabilities . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [227.2, 1182.0, 882.2, 1202.8]}, {"text": "$(257,913) $(238,910)", "bbox": [903.1, 1182.0, 1101.1, 1202.8]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2011, the Company had deferred tax assets arising from deductible temporary", "bbox": [185.5, 1240.2, 1008.5, 1261.1]}, {"text": "differences, tax losses, and tax credits of $151.7 million before the offset of certain deferred tax liabilities. With", "bbox": [143.8, 1265.2, 1078.5, 1286.1]}, {"text": "the exception of certain deferred tax assets related to book and tax bases differences of certain investments and", "bbox": [143.8, 1290.2, 1070.1, 1311.1]}, {"text": "certain foreign net operating loss carryforwards, management believes it is more likely than not that forecasted", "bbox": [143.8, 1315.2, 1069.5, 1336.1]}, {"text": "income, together with the tax effects of the deferred tax liabilities, will be sufficient to fully recover the", "bbox": [143.8, 1340.2, 1007.7, 1361.1]}, {"text": "remaining deferred tax assets. During 2011, the Company reduced its valuation allowance by $2.3 million. The", "bbox": [143.8, 1365.3, 1072.0, 1386.1]}, {"text": "reduction is primarily related to a release of a valuation allowance applied to foreign loss carryforwards as the", "bbox": [143.8, 1390.3, 1063.2, 1411.1]}, {"text": "Company is projecting sufficient future income to allow use of a portion of the foreign loss carryforward.", "bbox": [143.8, 1415.3, 1024.6, 1436.1]}, {"text": "Š", "bbox": [1173.9, 492.4, 1198.9, 506.3]}, {"text": "101", "bbox": [603.4, 1465.8, 634.6, 1486.6]}, {"text": "Form 10-K", "bbox": [1174.6, 362.4, 1199.6, 481.3]}]}